{"tid":2009156,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"到底VIU個升級服務點取消…仲難搞過有線","createTime":"2020-05-09T14:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T07:00:46.000Z","uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67fc4edc21f5f4b86ba77ca1aeddc8ef86c6e468","tid":2009156,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"當初以為好似Netflix咁容易訂又容易取消<br />\n點知今日想取消時先發現原來取消要好撚柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘唔係我訂，而係我老婆用iphone訂，訂完又唔撚識取消走嚟問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係佢部iphone碌來碌去都搵唔撚到點樣取消訂購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nViu真係好撚柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩年代呀取消個服務都可以複雜到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac3e8ff448d473109bc7b373f13e0feec66fa26","tid":2009156,"uid":277366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6 . 取消付費Viu升級會員服務訂購<br />\n<br />\n6.1除非在訂購服務時另有說明，您可以隨時取消您的付費Viu 升級會員服務訂購，您仍可繼續享有服務，直到下一個結算日期之前的日曆天。<br />\n6.2 取消：<br />\n6.2.1若您通過直接付款（為避免疑問，與第6.2.2條所述的其他第三方網關相反）支付訂購的Viu升級會員服務，請前往「我的資料」頁面並按照指示取消，並必須在下個結算日開始計算前的最少二十四（24）小時完成取消。如您取消訂購升級會員服務，您的Viu升級會員服務將於目前收費週期結束時自動暫停。若要查看您的付費升級會員服務訂購的到期日，請點選「我的資料」頁面。<br />\n6.2.2 若您通過App Store或Google Play支付訂購的Viu升級會員服務，則需要透過該支付網關取消，並必須在下個結算日開始計算前的最少二十四（24）小時完成取消。例如前往適用的第三方帳戶，關閉自動續訂功能，或透過該第三方取消訂購Viu升級會員服務。您也可前往適用的第三方帳戶，查看您的 Viu升級會員服務收費資訊。<br />\nApp Store跟Google Play用戶，請瀏覽以下連結以獲得更多詳細資訊：<br />\nApp Store: <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT202039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT202039&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpTeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=950e0345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT202039</a><br />\nGoogle Play: <a href=\"https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/7018481?co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid&amp;hl=zh-HK&amp;oco=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fgoogleplay%2Fanswer%2F7018481%3Fco%3DGENIE.Platform%253DAndroid%26hl%3Dzh-HK%26oco%3D1&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpTeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=81d4a375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/7018481?co=GENIE.Platform%3DAndroid&amp;hl=zh-HK&amp;oco=1</a>"},{"pid":"45a6d281220096a3e6b076788239f7a45f1da080","tid":2009156,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dac3e8ff448d473109bc7b373f13e0feec66fa26","tid":2009156,"uid":277366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6 . 取消付費Viu升級會員服務訂購<br />\n<br />\n6.1除非在訂購服務時另有說明，您可以隨時取消您的付費Viu 升級會員服務訂購，您仍可繼續享有服務，直到下一個結算日期之前的日曆天。<br />\n6.2 取消：<br />\n6.2.1若您通過直接付款（為避免疑問，與第6.2.2條所述的其他第三方網關相反）支付訂購的Viu升級會員服務，請前往「我的資料」頁面並按照指示取消，並必須在下個結算日開始計算前的最少二十四（24）小時完成取消。如您取消訂購升級會員服務，您的Viu升級會員服務將於目前收費週期結束時自動暫停。若要查看您的付費升級會員服務訂購的到期日，請點選「我的資料」頁面。<br 